782
01:00:50,823 --> 01:00:55,202
<i>Karena itu, semua anggota staf
diharapkan berpartisipasi.</i>

783
01:00:55,411 --> 01:00:56,787
<i>Harap diingat</i>

784
01:00:56,870 --> 01:01:00,249
